Looking for fun
. I prefer single men, 35 and older, lives in austin and surrounding metro areas
. and not looking for anything serious. Someone who can respect a lady. 
Please be mindful...I am a lady therefore need to get to trust you before I will meet with you. Also I don't give out my phone number till I'm ready to do so, so please be respectful...dating sites are here to meet people and chat on here for the time being.
I love watching movies especially classics. I love to listen to classic rock and the old music.
I enjoy playing darts and billiards. There's a lot more about me but if I tell all now, there wouldn't be much to talk about except daily rituals. So send me a message and we can go from there. Thanks for stopping by and have a wonderful day. Medicinal Hemp Friendly
